在gradle android 标签下面的子标签添加下面的代码就可以了
        buildConfigField "boolean", "TINKER_ENABLE", "${tinkerpatchSupport.tinkerEnable}"


例如： 
android {
    defaultConfig {
        buildConfigField "boolean", "TINKER_ENABLE", "${tinkerpatchSupport.tinkerEnable}"
    }
}
or
        buildConfigField("String", "SOURCE", "\"AsafaActive\"")
or
